Package: AEGIS
Type: Package
Title: Audit and Evaluate deconvolution outputs in Grid-based Spatial transcriptomics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: AEGIS Team [aut, cre]
Maintainer: AEGIS Team <team@example.org>
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "AEGIS", family = "Team", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "team@example.org")
    )
Description: A lightweight MVP package for auditing and comparing spatial transcriptomics
    deconvolution outputs on Seurat objects. It provides utilities to load 10x
    Visium data, simulate deconvolution matrices, run quality audits, compare
    methods, compute a consensus estimate, generate figures, and render an HTML
    report.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/JamesWu7/AEGIS
BugReports: https://github.com/JamesWu7/AEGIS/issues
